        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 A18 Pro vs A17 Pro 晶片跑分结果比对　效能提升约 18%、媲美 M1 Mac Mini</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/a18-pro-better-than-17-pro-18/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=a18-pro-better-than-17-pro-18</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/a18-pro-better-than-17-pro-18/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple A17 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple A18 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 16 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262570</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Geekbench 今日发表了 iPhone 16 Pro 系列采用的 A18 Pro 晶片跑分测试，结果显示 ，无论是单核或是多核跑分表现，A18 Pro 晶片均优于 A17 Pro 晶片 18%。据外媒引述数据指，A18 Pro 晶片效能更可与 2020 年 Mac Mini M1 晶片媲美。</p><p>Apple 发布 iPhone 16 时表示 A18 Pro 晶片比 A17 Pro 晶片快 15%，而根据 Geekbench 测试结果显示，A18 Pro 晶片比 A17 Pro 快约 18%，与 Apple 官方数据相差无几。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleeventseptember9-109-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleeventseptember9-109-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleeventseptember9-109.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 官方数据指 A18 Pro 比 A17 Pro 快了 15%，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uarNiSl_uh4&amp;ab_channel=Apple">Apple@YouTube</a></p><h2>A17、18 Pro 单／多核心跑分结果</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;"></td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;"><strong>单核心跑分</strong></td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;"><strong>多核心跑分</strong></td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;"><strong>A17 Pro（平均值）</strong></td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">2,896</td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">7,192</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;"><strong>A18 Pro（单次测试）</strong></td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">3,409（<span style="color: #339966;"><strong>+17.7%</strong></span>）</td><td style="width: 33.3333%; text-align: center; height: 24px;">8,492（<span style="color: #339966;"><strong>+18.08%</strong></span>）</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190936-692x580.jpg" alt="" width="692" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190936-692x580.jpg 692w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190936.jpg 927w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 692px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 15 Pro 的单、多核心跑分成绩，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/ios_devices/iphone-15-pro">Geekbench</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190949-694x292.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="292" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190949-694x292.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912190949.jpg 938w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 16 Pro 的单、多核心跑分成绩，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/ios_devices/iphone-15-pro">Geekbench</a></p><p>根据 Geekbench 数据显示，2020 年推出的 M1 Mac Mini 单核跑分成绩为 2,362，多核跑分成绩为 8,447，可见 A18 Pro 单核心效能（跑分成绩为 3,409 分）已胜过 4 年前推出的 M1 Mac Mini，而多核心效能则是不相伯仲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912193505-596x580.jpg" alt="" width="596" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912193505-596x580.jpg 596w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912193505.jpg 924w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 596px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A18 Pro 与 2020 年推出的 M1 Mac Mini 效能相若，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/macs/mac-mini-late-2020">Geekbench</a></p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_236 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_1 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_236"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"></div></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/7714134">Geekbench</a>、<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/09/11/a18-pro-chip-geekbench-benchmark-result/">Mac Rumors</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手评测，港人最爱 18 个功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/04/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%e6%a8%a1%e5%9e%8b%e6%a9%9f%e9%96%8b%e7%ae%b1-%e6%8f%ad-5-%e5%a4%a7%e6%96%b0%e6%94%b9%e5%8b%95%e4%bd%8d/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列模型机开箱，揭 5 大新改动位</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/all-iphone-16-models-45w-fast-charging-wired/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">有线充电功率曝光，全线 iPhone 16 型号支援 45W 快充</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/a18-pro-better-than-17-pro-18/mobile-phone/">iPhone 16 A18 Pro vs A17 Pro 晶片跑分结果比对　效能提升约 18%、媲美 M1 Mac Mini</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
