        <item>
            <title>华为 Mate XT 三折机炒价见 22 万港元　预订开放 3 日接 550 万部订单</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/huawei-mate-xt-200k-rmb/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-mate-xt-200k-rmb</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/huawei-mate-xt-200k-rmb/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:00:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为 Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262553</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前华为发布了全新旗舰三折叠手机 Mate XT 非凡大师，2 日前我们报道过预购额已达 200 万部，甚至有二手平台表示愿意基于原价额外加 1.6 万元收机（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/09/huawei-mate-xt-2mill-order/fun-tech/">相关报道</a>）。今日小编浏览华为商城发现，现时 Mate XT 已经有近 550 万预订订单，中国著名二手平台「闲鱼」上亦有不少华为 Mate XT 放盘，最高惊见 19.9 万元人民币（约港币 21.90 万元）</p><p>距离预约结束仍有 7 日，华为商城今日下午 6 点半数据显示，目前已有 549.7 万人预订 Mate XT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1.jpg 1212w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲目前已经有 549.7 万人次预订华为 Mate XT， 图片来源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/comdetail/index.html?prdId=10086499369393">VMALL</a></p><p>中国最大的二手物品交易平台「闲鱼」可见，华为 Mate XT 售价由原价至 5 万元不等，其中最高售价惊见 19.99 万元人民币（约港币 21.9 万元），仍然有 3 个人表示有兴趣购买。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">Goofish</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239-368x580.jpg" alt="" width="368" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239-368x580.jpg 368w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239.jpg 571w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 368px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高惊见人民币 19.99 万元，图片来源：<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">Goofish</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/comdetail/index.html?prdId=10086499369393">华为商城</a>、<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">闲鱼</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/huaweimatextud-firstlook/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei Mate XT Ultimate Design 非凡大师现场评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/huawei-mate-xt-ultimate-design-kirin-9010/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 Mate XT 处理器确认，效能被指属中阶水平</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/how-to-talk-on-huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 Mate XT 三折机应如何听电话　网民：招摇过市易招贼</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/huawei-mate-xt-200k-rmb/mobile-phone/">华为 Mate XT 三折机炒价见 22 万港元　预订开放 3 日接 550 万部订单</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
